Use pnpm for package management. Package versions should be pinned.
Use kebab-case for file names. Use PascalCase for component names. Use camelCase for variable names. Use SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE for environment variables.

Export variables or functions only if they are used outside of the file.
Functions expressions preferred with arrow function syntax.
No default exports apart except in situations where it is mandatory. Use named exports/imports
No barrel files.
One utility function per file.

Prefer code duplications over early or wrong abstractions. Use WET(Write Everything Twice) approach.